name: Key Details
description:
Maples keys are caught among grapevine tendrils in winter. The details of the vascular system are back lit and made visible by the fresh bright snow. 

Photographed 2017. GIF Created 2021. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing and GIF building.

1024x685 GIF

Winter GIF Series: 3/3
